data.description: Investors Alert!! 3 bedroom 2 bath home in the beautiful, sought after subdivision of Tomoka Oak!! Lot is almost half an Acre with plenty of backyard space. The roof was replaced in 2016, and the garage door was installed in 2017. There is an Eat-In-Kitchen, Formal Living Room, Dining Room, and a nice open Den with sliders out to the backyard. The home needs updates inside, but is in a great location. It is being sold in As-Is condition. Please email for inside pictures.
